skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hop me
des:
Live to travel skill help the user to know about the best 5 places to visit for their cities. 
Supported cities include:
Bangalore,
Chennai, 
Coimbatore, 
New Delhi, 
Mumbai,
Kolkata, 
Pune, 
Kochi,
Hyderabad,
Ahmadabad,
Visakhapatnam,
Surat,
Jaipur,
Kanpur,
Lucknow,
Nagpur,
Ghaziabad,
Madurai

This skill supports only Indian cities.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
